{"tid":379163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遲到逼員工扣假補鐘　機場保安公司涉違法","createTime":"2017-08-29T05:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T02:58:55.000Z","uid":20933,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61fb768b86c93914ada5d1fbe717bb14b40bfb5f","tid":379163,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:24:57.000Z","msg":"強颱風「天鴿」日前直襲本港，落波過後，路面交通仍有一段時間未能完全恢復，不少打工仔不能上班或遲到，但有工會指，機場保安公司（AVSECO）毫不體恤員工，要求遲到或缺勤的員工簽同意書，聲明自願扣減累積假期或補回工時，涉違反勞工法例。<br />\n<br />\n香港民用航空事業職工總會指，機場巴士班次疏落，保安上班路途遙遠，但公司卻扣減員工的年假、法定假日或休息日，用來補償因8號或以上風球未能上班而損失的工作時間，是不合理、不合法。工會強烈譴責機場保安公司扣減員工累積假期，違反勞工法例，工會將跟進機場保安的投訴。"},{"pid":"fca1c41ab477cc5b02e38ff2ac8cbf7ac0ef7fcf","tid":379163,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:25:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170829&amp;guid=57140958&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170829%26guid%3D57140958%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=NCCDkho3GobewTXrfFF8TROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=a3f80a6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170829%26guid%3D57140958%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=d32c6940\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170829&amp;guid=57140958&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"4c85f261a00b8805bb8e254be936aa912403fb08","tid":379163,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:25:47.000Z","msg":"avseco 正仆街"},{"pid":"3abaa1beb23777120cad6a1c2f6e8997801cc2bf","tid":379163,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:26:09.000Z","msg":"老闆：住係機場就唔洗遲到啦，死蠢"},{"pid":"1db992e97a55b26eda96cb47cb672be49efca473","tid":379163,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:30:49.000Z","m